title: essinth furryart january 2007
description:
Essinth&#039;s Furry Art Collection. January 2007.

The best of the best, from Essinth&#039;s point of view. If the picture&#039;s content is good, but drawn badly, it gets trashed. If the picture is drawn well but that&#039;s just it - only drawn well, it gets trashed, too. 

The collection is categorised, 0 means non-adult and mostly safe for work, everything above - adult. Which category picture belongs to was intuitively chosen, no strict rules.
